title: ISic000571. I.Sicily inscription 000571
body:
Facsimile Images

D(is) ((·)) m(anibus)
Suetia ((·)) Tyndaris
vix(it) ((·)) an(nis) ((·)) LXI
menses ((·)) I ((·)) dies ((·)) XVIII

Apparatus criticus

Text of CIL

English translation

Sacred to the spirits of the dead. Suetia Tyndaris lived for 61 years, one month and 18 days.

Italian translation

Sacro agli spiriti dei defunti. Suetia Tyndaris visse per 61 anni, un mese e 18 giorni.
